      "widgets_values": [
        "Figure 1: A young Asian man in ancient attire, with black hair, wearing a cyan robe and jade ornaments, realistic natural texture.\nFigure 2: A young Asian woman in ancient attire, with black hair in a bun, wearing a light blue wide-sleeve long dress and a jade hairpin, realistic natural texture.\nFigure 3: Classical Chinese garden, stone pavilion, lotus pond with koi fish, stone bridge, pink cherry blossoms and bamboo forest, realistic natural texture.\n\n",
        "In a classical Chinese garden, a stone pavilion spans across a lotus pond. The water surface is covered with pink and white lotus flowers and swimming red and white koi. Outside the pavilion, a winding stone bridge leads toward the scene. In the distance, mountains rise behind a bamboo forest blooming with cherry blossoms. The color palette is warm, golden, and soft. The camera is positioned at a side-front medium shot, locked on the scene. Male A, dressed in a deep cyan robe, stands on the stone bridge on the left side of the frame. His hands rest naturally at his sides as he slowly walks onto the bridge, his wide sleeves swaying gently in the breeze. He stops at the stone railing outside the pavilion, his gaze lowered toward the koi swimming in the water. Female A, wearing a light blue wide-sleeve long dress, sits cross-legged at a stone table inside the pavilion on the right side of the frame. Her hands rest lightly on an ancient guqin placed horizontally on the table, facing the camera. Ripples spread across the pond as the koi swim gracefully, and dappled sunlight filters through the pavilion roof.\n\nMale A walks slowly onto the stone bridge, his wide sleeves swaying gently. He stands by the railing outside the pavilion, his eyes fixed on the koi swimming in the water. The camera slowly pushes in by 18%.\n\nMale A walks steadily from the stone bridge into the pavilion and comes to a stop beside Female A.\n\nFemale A pauses her hands on the guqin strings, slowly lowers them, and glances up at Male A before gently touching the strings again.\nFemale A (gently reassuring, soft and soothing, sweet and tender tone): \"You're here.\"\nMale A (calmly, in a steady, cool tone): \"I am.\"\n\nThe koi continue to swim in the pond, lotus leaves sway softly, and sunlight shimmers on the water's surface.",
        "",
        0.0011
      ]
    },
